  "3287200": {
    "name": "Bluebie VS The Army of Cyborgs",
    "steam_appid": 3287200,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/7b3afe4059297a26dcf22478e874f5f0.avif?t=1767188814\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras_big/7b3afe4059297a26dcf22478e874f5f0.avif?t=1767188814 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bluebie VS the Army of Cyborgs is a Cartoony 3D platformer that will take you to the fictive world of planet  Rebaga. The planet look pretty much like earth and the culture there is pretty similar to ours. One day, Cybex, a self made Cyborg, decided to invade the planet and turn its inhabitants into his servants.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course, Bluebie, a farmer, is not willing to see his planet enslaved by the army of Cybex and decided to fight back and free the prisoners Cybex took.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In his quest, Bluebie will travel through mines,  mountains, desert and different other places where the cyborgs settled and launched their operation. He will fight the generals of Dr Cybex to free as much prisoners as he can while developing and purchasing new skills thanks to his colorful closet plenty of different outfits.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight Enemies</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A stick, a spear, a boomerang, a slingshot, a crossbow and a pigeon launcher. Which weapon to use to fight your enemies. Every weapon will have its own range and damage level. One is sometimes enough, two or more could be a necessity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/3849a560247af8e239f90958ccac92bf.poster.avif?t=1767188814\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/3849a560247af8e239f90958ccac92bf.webm?t=1767188814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/3849a560247af8e239f90958ccac92bf.mp4?t=1767188814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Release The  Prisoners</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The army of Cybex has taken many people. The cages might be hidden allover the places. Try to free them all to get the biggest achievement of the game, an achievement to rule them all, The Freeyorator !!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/284c6411260044b53ef4d8747d4687df.poster.avif?t=1767188814\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/284c6411260044b53ef4d8747d4687df.webm?t=1767188814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/284c6411260044b53ef4d8747d4687df.mp4?t=1767188814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Change Your Outfit</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can choose your outfit in the main menu or within the game, all you need to do is to access a fitting room and choose the best fit of the moment !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/c7c6d2e3abf29581f168093ef583873b.poster.avif?t=1767188814\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/c7c6d2e3abf29581f168093ef583873b.webm?t=1767188814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/c7c6d2e3abf29581f168093ef583873b.mp4?t=1767188814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Execute Missions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every level will come with its own riddles, challenges and missions. Execute these missions to move forward. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/3a3baa7de51a31c548648c932bd1dcb5.poster.avif?t=1767188814\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/3a3baa7de51a31c548648c932bd1dcb5.webm?t=1767188814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/3a3baa7de51a31c548648c932bd1dcb5.mp4?t=1767188814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Enjoy Your Rides</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether it is to avoid enemies, moving faster or for fun , you will be able to ride animals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is also an aircraft level where you will have to fight enemy aircrafts and air defenses within a timeframe. A race against time, a race against the enemy.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/6f061cb93bbc358eb674864aa57b4a2c.poster.avif?t=1767188814\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/6f061cb93bbc358eb674864aa57b4a2c.webm?t=1767188814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/6f061cb93bbc358eb674864aa57b4a2c.mp4?t=1767188814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Get New Skills</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your experience points are collected by killing enemies. To unlock new skills, you will have to kill whatever enemy you find and collect diamonds to  get the biggest ones so... you know what you got to do when you got to do it... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/f7ad4176b31d7119ffab6269b4dd77d7.poster.avif?t=1767188814\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/f7ad4176b31d7119ffab6269b4dd77d7.webm?t=1767188814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/f7ad4176b31d7119ffab6269b4dd77d7.mp4?t=1767188814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Weapon Shops To Refill</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're short of projectiles or you want to acquire new skills, no problem, we got you! Every level will have at least two weapon shops to buy projectiles for your weapons, or to acquire new skills, thanks to the diamonds you collected previously. Just collect as much as you can, some items might be expensive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/f93b26e87cf2d03735df904e93b0396e.poster.avif?t=1767188814\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/f93b26e87cf2d03735df904e93b0396e.webm?t=1767188814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287200/extras/f93b26e87cf2d03735df904e93b0396e.mp4?t=1767188814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
